00:02:09.870 --> 00:02:10.380
Get up!

00:02:10.520 --> 00:02:11.150
Step aside!

00:02:11.150 --> 00:02:11.960
Excuse me.

00:02:13.080 --> 00:02:13.870
Come on.

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:14.840
Stop watching!

