00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:29.680
I asked her all night—

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:30.540
still the same.

00:02:30.710 --> 00:02:31.910
She said she didn't see the suspect,

00:02:31.910 --> 00:02:32.840
only the body.

00:02:33.310 --> 00:02:34.840
It even gave her a heart attack.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:35.470
Yes.

00:02:44.079 --> 00:02:44.610
Make way!

00:02:45.150 --> 00:02:45.750
Make way!

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:46.840
Make way! Make way!

00:02:46.840 --> 00:02:47.360
Stop pushing.

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:48.280
We're working a case—no entry.

00:02:48.280 --> 00:02:48.910
We're from the Criminal Police Team.

00:02:48.910 --> 00:02:50.280
We're one of you.

00:02:52.430 --> 00:02:52.870
Song!

00:02:53.590 --> 00:02:54.150
He's inside.

00:02:54.150 --> 00:02:55.190
Stop asking, okay?

00:02:55.190 --> 00:02:55.610
Chief.

00:02:55.750 --> 00:02:57.150
We'd tell you if we could.

00:03:01.280 --> 00:03:02.680
Have you identified her?

00:03:02.800 --> 00:03:03.680
She's in the water;

00:03:03.680 --> 00:03:04.680
we can't tell her.

00:03:04.960 --> 00:03:05.630
I think

00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:07.030
we should get the body out first.

00:03:07.030 --> 00:03:09.030
There are more and more people here.

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:11.030
Is there any trace at the scene?

00:03:11.030 --> 00:03:11.830
It's pouring;

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:13.520
the rain's washed any traces away.

00:03:13.520 --> 00:03:14.580
Pump the water out.

00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:16.870
Do it.

00:03:32.030 --> 00:03:32.870
Stop pushing.

00:03:33.030 --> 00:03:34.079
What are you pushing for?

00:03:34.079 --> 00:03:35.810
Go home and wash the water tank.

00:03:35.960 --> 00:03:37.680
The body has been stewing in the well

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:39.340
long enough to turn into soup.

00:03:42.000 --> 00:03:43.079
Go home.

00:03:44.079 --> 00:03:44.810
My goodness.

00:03:49.030 --> 00:03:50.290
Why did you go in again?

00:03:50.400 --> 00:03:51.470
I want to go in and take a look.

00:03:51.470 --> 00:03:52.560
There are so many people inside.

00:03:52.560 --> 00:03:53.690
Don't make it worse.

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:54.960
Stay outside.

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:15.120
Hello,

00:05:15.190 --> 00:05:15.720
show me your ID.

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:16.920
Did you see

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:18.120
anyone suspicious

00:05:18.270 --> 00:05:18.750
on the night of May 18th?

00:05:18.750 --> 00:05:19.310
Think about it.

00:05:19.310 --> 00:05:20.310
Aunt, if there's nothing else,

00:05:20.310 --> 00:05:22.040
-Don't look here.
-That night,

00:05:22.040 --> 00:05:24.040
I slept better than any other night.

00:05:24.070 --> 00:05:25.480
I didn't hear anything.

00:05:25.750 --> 00:05:27.310
Did you see anyone suspicious?

00:05:27.310 --> 00:05:28.160
I was home sleeping.

00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:29.190
Just tell me.

00:05:29.270 --> 00:05:30.330
I went to bed early.

00:05:32.470 --> 00:05:33.190
Excuse me.

00:05:34.680 --> 00:05:35.480
Captain Song!

00:05:36.120 --> 00:05:36.800
How's it going?

00:05:36.800 --> 00:05:38.159
The victim's father, Liu Aijun,

00:05:38.159 --> 00:05:39.040
fired a few people

00:05:39.040 --> 00:05:40.310
when the factory restructured.

00:05:40.310 --> 00:05:41.680
Those guys are suspects.

00:05:41.680 --> 00:05:43.010
We're looking for them.

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:43.920
Did he see the victim

00:05:43.920 --> 00:05:44.680
last night?

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:45.600
No.

00:05:46.270 --> 00:05:47.360
I heard he's the stepfather, right?

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:48.120
Yes.

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:49.750
How's their relationship?

00:05:49.750 --> 00:05:51.240
They've always been close.

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:52.560
I checked and he's basically cleared.

00:05:52.560 --> 00:05:53.240
And last night

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:54.159
he was working late at the factory

00:05:54.159 --> 00:05:55.000
with his secretary.

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:55.480
Have the meeting first.

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.140
Secretary?

00:05:56.920 --> 00:05:58.040
His female secretary.

00:05:58.040 --> 00:06:00.170
They've been together for half a year.

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:01.680
She provided an alibi too.

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.540
Is this female secretary single?

00:06:03.920 --> 00:06:04.480
Yes.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:05.560
Liu,

00:06:05.800 --> 00:06:06.310
Zhang,

00:06:06.830 --> 00:06:08.360
you two go over this thoroughly.

00:06:08.360 --> 00:06:09.090
-Okay.
-Yes.

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:11.690
Here's what I think:

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:13.430
let's use

00:06:13.560 --> 00:06:15.270
our local know-how;

00:06:15.510 --> 00:06:16.750
check whether anyone unfamiliar

00:06:16.750 --> 00:06:18.240
has shown up in the precinct recently.

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:18.900
Generally,

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:19.950
when a newcomer shows up around here,

00:06:19.950 --> 00:06:20.920
we patrol officers

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:22.380
figure it out pretty fast.

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:24.330
Who's the cop in this precinct?

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:25.560
Ran.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:29.920
Ran Xi?

00:06:32.750 --> 00:06:33.560
Ran Xi!

00:06:40.190 --> 00:06:41.560
I didn't recognize you.

00:06:41.560 --> 00:06:42.070
Well...

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:45.400
Look how many years it's been
since we last met.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:46.120
Back then,

00:06:46.310 --> 00:06:48.040
I was Little Song, he was Little Ran.

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:50.360
We've known for many years,
and we're now getting old.

00:06:50.360 --> 00:06:51.620
You're in this office.

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:53.270
Hello, Captain Song.

00:06:55.310 --> 00:06:55.750
Ran,

00:06:55.930 --> 00:06:57.310
you are a veteran detective,

00:06:57.310 --> 00:06:57.870
right?

00:06:58.310 --> 00:07:00.310
Share your thoughts with everyone.

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:04.800
I fully support
the Criminal Police Team's work.

00:07:04.800 --> 00:07:06.930
I'm asking you to share your thoughts.

00:07:10.510 --> 00:07:11.390
Guess I'm just unlucky—

00:07:11.390 --> 00:07:13.050
—had to happen in my precinct.

00:07:13.310 --> 00:07:14.840
What are you talking about?

00:07:15.870 --> 00:07:17.430
I mean, the girl is unlucky.

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:20.040
Ran is testing us.

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:22.270
In my opinion,

00:07:22.750 --> 00:07:24.510
the suspect probably meant to rape her,

00:07:24.510 --> 00:07:25.240
but got angry

00:07:25.430 --> 00:07:26.630
when she resisted.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:27.390
In the end,

00:07:27.390 --> 00:07:28.850
he threw her into the well.

00:07:29.190 --> 00:07:30.590
She must've fought back,

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:31.740
otherwise she wouldn't have been killed.

00:07:31.740 --> 00:07:32.400
Yeah, yeah.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:33.040
No.

00:07:34.240 --> 00:07:35.640
I don't think it was rape.

00:07:35.950 --> 00:07:37.630
If it were,
he wouldn't have been so violent.

00:07:37.630 --> 00:07:38.480
And her wallet

00:07:38.480 --> 00:07:39.280
wasn't taken,

00:07:39.310 --> 00:07:41.240
so we can rule out robbery.

00:07:41.830 --> 00:07:42.950
Either it's a crime of passion

00:07:42.950 --> 00:07:44.000
or a revenge killing.

00:07:44.000 --> 00:07:45.190
Start investigating along those two lines.

00:07:45.190 --> 00:07:45.680
Okay.

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:48.050
What did her mother say?

00:07:48.190 --> 00:07:49.480
Her mother is Huang Hui,

00:07:49.480 --> 00:07:51.270
the union chair

00:07:51.310 --> 00:07:52.909
at the electronics factory.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:55.000
She's a bit difficult to deal with.

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:55.720
What do you mean?

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:57.070
She refuses to acknowledge the body,

00:07:57.070 --> 00:07:58.560
and won't let anyone else either.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:00.270
Then how was the identity confirmed?

00:08:00.270 --> 00:08:01.930
Name was on her school papers.

00:08:02.310 --> 00:08:03.560
It's a bit troublesome

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:04.510
if the family doesn't identify the body.

00:08:04.510 --> 00:08:05.000
Yes.

00:08:05.830 --> 00:08:06.390
Ran!

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:08.280
Think of a way.

00:08:11.680 --> 00:08:12.240
Chief Zhu,

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:13.480
Tian Hao and Mei showed up,

00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:15.410
insisting their daughter is dead.

00:08:15.750 --> 00:08:17.160
It happened in my precinct.

00:08:17.160 --> 00:08:18.160
I'll go handle it.

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:23.130
Will you keep your promise?

00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:24.040
No.

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:25.510
You really expect me to believe that?

00:08:25.510 --> 00:08:26.720
Don't touch me!

00:08:26.830 --> 00:08:27.480
What are you doing?

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:28.360
If you can stop me here,

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:29.820
can you stop me over there?

00:08:29.830 --> 00:08:30.510
Look,

00:08:30.600 --> 00:08:31.800
if you don't give me a real lead today,

00:08:31.800 --> 00:08:32.960
a real lead today,

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:33.030
[Speak openly. We'll listen.
Be honest. We'll understand.]

00:08:33.030 --> 00:08:34.789
I'll smash my head
against this wall and die.

00:08:34.789 --> 00:08:37.030
You have to
close her household record today.

00:08:37.030 --> 00:08:37.630
Ran,

00:08:37.909 --> 00:08:39.120
is the body our Chang?

00:08:39.390 --> 00:08:40.750
I saw the body.

00:08:41.240 --> 00:08:42.500
She had that long hair.

00:08:43.150 --> 00:08:45.280
You really think it's your Tian Chang?

00:08:47.120 --> 00:08:48.360
Wait, Ran,

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:49.480
is it true?

00:08:49.960 --> 00:08:51.270
Why would I lie to you?

00:08:51.270 --> 00:08:52.080
Ran said so.

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:52.670
You...

00:08:52.720 --> 00:08:53.670
Thank you, Ran.

00:08:54.150 --> 00:08:54.910
Then you

00:08:55.510 --> 00:08:56.310
go back first.

00:08:56.360 --> 00:08:57.600
Please

00:08:57.600 --> 00:08:59.200
help us keep looking for her.

00:09:00.030 --> 00:09:01.320
Thank you.

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.820
She died a pretty horrible death.

00:09:05.080 --> 00:09:06.410
Judging from the wound,

00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:08.360
it looks like one clean slash
across the neck,

00:09:08.360 --> 00:09:09.550
cut through the windpipe

00:09:09.550 --> 00:09:10.350
and in the end,

00:09:10.390 --> 00:09:12.390
she choked to death on her own blood.

00:09:13.790 --> 00:09:15.850
Didn't anyone around hear anything?

00:09:16.550 --> 00:09:18.390
She couldn't even scream by then.

00:09:18.390 --> 00:09:20.600
The strangest part is, there was no semen.

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:21.530
The genital area

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:23.400
clearly shows signs of assault,

00:09:23.440 --> 00:09:24.870
but after a thorough check,

00:09:24.870 --> 00:09:26.080
we couldn't find any.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:27.360
What could have caused this?

00:09:27.360 --> 00:09:28.890
A relatively large object,

00:09:29.150 --> 00:09:29.840
smooth

00:09:30.080 --> 00:09:30.960
and hard.

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:32.360
A bottle?

00:09:32.550 --> 00:09:33.550
That's possible.

00:09:34.430 --> 00:09:35.870
[Outstanding Unit]

00:09:35.870 --> 00:09:36.930
What are you doing?

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:37.960
Sorry.

00:09:38.960 --> 00:09:39.840
He's a new cop from the CPPSC grad,

00:09:39.840 --> 00:09:41.100
always poking around.

00:09:41.360 --> 00:09:42.240
We've got one

00:09:42.360 --> 00:09:43.220
from there too.

00:09:43.550 --> 00:09:44.480
Are you two in the same year?

00:09:44.480 --> 00:09:45.240
Do you know each other?

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:45.480
Yes...

00:09:45.480 --> 00:09:46.000
No.

00:09:48.600 --> 00:09:50.010
Have you found the murder weapon?

00:09:50.010 --> 00:09:50.870
[Outstanding Unit]

00:09:50.870 --> 00:09:51.200
No.

00:09:51.200 --> 00:09:52.000
We, the Criminal Police Team,

00:09:52.000 --> 00:09:53.120
didn't find the weapon at the scene.

00:09:53.120 --> 00:09:53.870
Our men

00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:55.120
find a few suspicious knives

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.630
at the crime scene.

00:09:57.510 --> 00:09:58.030
Gan'e,

00:09:58.630 --> 00:09:59.870
bring the knives over.

00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:00.320
Okay.

00:10:11.710 --> 00:10:13.900
[Tool Room]

00:10:13.900 --> 00:10:14.500
Excuse me,

00:10:14.600 --> 00:10:16.460
where are the controlled knives?

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:22.120
I think we can rule out

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:22.750
Huang Hui.

00:10:22.960 --> 00:10:23.840
Let's check if Liu Aijun

00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:24.770
has any enemies.

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:27.650
This girl was in college after all,

00:10:27.790 --> 00:10:28.750
so we need to check

00:10:28.750 --> 00:10:30.810
her social connections thoroughly.

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.290
Wait… What's wrong with you today?

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.520
Don't tell me you're the killer.

00:10:59.030 --> 00:11:00.600
Why are you poking around like that?

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:01.030
It's okay.

00:11:01.030 --> 00:11:01.790
Go on.

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:02.720
Alright,

00:11:02.790 --> 00:11:03.870
we, the Criminal Police Team,

00:11:03.870 --> 00:11:05.150
will continue investigating

00:11:05.150 --> 00:11:06.410
along these two lines.

00:11:08.150 --> 00:11:08.750
Chief Zhu,

00:11:08.910 --> 00:11:10.270
have the local station officers

00:11:10.270 --> 00:11:11.270
help check if anyone nearby
with a criminal record

00:11:11.270 --> 00:11:12.670
could be involved,

00:11:12.720 --> 00:11:13.150
okay?

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.000
Then you guys

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:16.390
cooperate with the Criminal Police Team

00:11:16.390 --> 00:11:17.480
and sort out the issue

00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:18.000
with the knives first.

00:11:18.000 --> 00:11:18.270
Got it.

00:11:18.270 --> 00:11:18.670
Okay?

00:11:18.750 --> 00:11:20.120
Okay.

00:11:23.840 --> 00:11:24.270
Ran,

00:11:27.850 --> 00:11:29.790
[Meeting Room]

00:11:29.790 --> 00:11:31.000
this happened in your precinct.

00:11:31.000 --> 00:11:32.200
You have to take responsibility.

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:33.270
How am I supposed to take responsibility?

00:11:33.270 --> 00:11:34.790
Go ask yourself.

00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:35.070
Don't ask me.

00:11:35.070 --> 00:11:35.750
[Meeting Room]

00:11:35.750 --> 00:11:36.880
I'm not a detective.

00:11:37.440 --> 00:11:38.750
Someone's gone missing in my precinct.

00:11:38.750 --> 00:11:40.550
Didn't you see they're looking for me?

00:11:40.550 --> 00:11:42.280
Have Qigui and the others do it.

00:11:43.030 --> 00:11:44.690
Don't play this trick with me.

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:46.000
Regular police and detectives

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:46.170
both have law‑enforcement powers.

00:11:46.170 --> 00:11:47.270
[Meeting Room]

00:11:47.270 --> 00:11:48.480
Does your employee's card say

00:11:48.480 --> 00:11:50.120
you're not allowed to investigate?

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:51.980
Fine, then I'll just do my own job.

00:11:52.120 --> 00:11:54.450
There's no "just my job"
when you're a cop.

00:11:55.870 --> 00:11:57.120
Chief, I need to tell you something.

00:11:57.120 --> 00:11:57.630
I might...

00:11:57.630 --> 00:11:58.870
You have no say here.

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:02.150
This is a criminal case, a murder case.

00:12:02.150 --> 00:12:03.340
Does it have anything to do with you?

00:12:03.340 --> 00:12:03.360
[Meeting Room]

00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:04.420
It has to do with me!

00:12:05.200 --> 00:12:05.910
When I go up to the bureau later

00:12:05.910 --> 00:12:06.750
and take the scolding,

00:12:06.750 --> 00:12:07.750
you two go with me.

00:12:08.790 --> 00:12:09.320
Alright,

00:12:10.000 --> 00:12:11.120
I'll do whatever the Criminal Police Team

00:12:11.120 --> 00:12:11.790
tells me.

00:12:12.120 --> 00:12:13.250
I'll follow orders.

00:12:13.390 --> 00:12:13.870
Come on, Ran,

00:12:13.870 --> 00:12:14.750
are you really not giving me

00:12:14.750 --> 00:12:15.550
any face here?

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:18.900
Step aside.

00:12:19.510 --> 00:12:22.850
[Meeting Room]

00:12:23.630 --> 00:12:25.510
How long has it been?

00:12:25.600 --> 00:12:26.930
Can't you just let it go?

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:28.870
Look,

00:12:29.240 --> 00:12:30.360
as long as I'm in this station,

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:31.000
we will not

00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:32.660
let people look down on us.

00:12:34.030 --> 00:12:36.120
Where's your sense of collective honor?

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:38.120
How about showing some initiative?

00:12:38.270 --> 00:12:39.930
Does every veteran detective

00:12:40.000 --> 00:12:41.000
who comes here just burn out

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:41.930
after a few days?

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:44.960
Do we really have
such a high burnout rate here?

00:12:47.440 --> 00:12:47.910
Got it.

00:12:48.580 --> 00:12:49.150
Got it.

00:12:49.750 --> 00:12:50.840
Do it.

00:12:50.840 --> 00:12:52.030
Make me proud.

00:12:52.550 --> 00:12:53.840
Got it, Chief.

00:12:55.080 --> 00:12:56.610
What were you trying to say?

00:12:56.670 --> 00:12:57.000
Chief.

00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:57.400
Chief.

00:12:57.870 --> 00:12:59.150
I need to talk to you.

00:12:59.440 --> 00:13:00.170
Okay, got it.

00:13:01.240 --> 00:13:02.270
You two,

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:04.030
get the victim's family here
to ID the body, now.

00:13:04.030 --> 00:13:04.750
What's this about them

00:13:04.750 --> 00:13:06.550
refusing to sign the paperwork?

00:13:38.030 --> 00:13:39.480
Hello, officers.

00:13:40.150 --> 00:13:40.750
Come in.

00:13:41.150 --> 00:13:42.000
I'm tied up right now,

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:43.200
so just sit anywhere.

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:54.970
Are you busy?

00:13:56.600 --> 00:13:57.910
Are you coming for Liu Ke?

00:13:57.910 --> 00:13:59.170
It's nothing serious.

00:13:59.480 --> 00:14:01.010
Why are you two coming here?

00:14:09.630 --> 00:14:10.150
Aijun.

00:14:16.630 --> 00:14:18.160
Are these Liu Ke's clothes?

00:14:18.510 --> 00:14:19.150
She

00:14:19.240 --> 00:14:20.270
never liked wearing his uniform.

00:14:20.270 --> 00:14:21.270
She'd shove it anywhere.

00:14:21.270 --> 00:14:22.670
Look, it's all wrinkled.

00:14:24.870 --> 00:14:26.330
Can you look for her again?

00:14:26.390 --> 00:14:27.000
Maybe she

00:14:27.000 --> 00:14:28.600
went to a classmate's place.

00:14:29.190 --> 00:14:30.270
She's always like this;

00:14:30.270 --> 00:14:32.000
she never stayed home for long.

00:14:32.790 --> 00:14:35.520
You were the same way back in school,
weren't you?

00:14:36.360 --> 00:14:37.560
Check the arcade too,

00:14:38.630 --> 00:14:41.150
she loves hanging around there.
She's such a tomboy—

00:14:41.150 --> 00:14:42.010
picks things up

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:43.390
so fast,

00:14:49.030 --> 00:14:49.790
Actually...

00:14:52.630 --> 00:14:53.600
Would you please come back

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:54.860
to the station with us?

00:14:59.030 --> 00:15:00.690
We'll need your cooperation.

00:15:05.270 --> 00:15:06.330
This got burned...

00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:14.120
Oh my god. This...

00:15:14.790 --> 00:15:15.250
This...

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:16.510
This...

00:15:16.870 --> 00:15:18.670
How's she supposed to wear this?

00:15:19.000 --> 00:15:19.670
Seriously…

00:15:21.550 --> 00:15:22.440
My God…

00:15:22.850 --> 00:15:24.000
What a joke.

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:26.250
Just cut it off.

00:15:26.720 --> 00:15:27.750
It's gonna have to be done
sooner or later anyway—

00:15:27.750 --> 00:15:29.330
might as well get it over with.

00:15:29.330 --> 00:15:30.070
How about this?

00:15:30.070 --> 00:15:30.910
Come with me

00:15:34.170 --> 00:15:36.370
back to the station and sign the papers.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:38.570
Where are you going?

00:15:42.240 --> 00:15:43.760
Where are you going so late?

00:15:43.760 --> 00:15:45.510
He will come with us
to the police station.

00:15:45.510 --> 00:15:47.600
Why are you going?

00:15:48.420 --> 00:15:49.650
What for?

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:51.290
-Who do you think you are?
-Stop beating him.

00:15:51.290 --> 00:15:52.290
Stop beating him.

00:15:52.510 --> 00:15:53.040
Get lost!

00:15:53.630 --> 00:15:54.160
Get lost!

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:56.250
Who allows you to go?

00:15:56.360 --> 00:15:56.910
Aijun,

00:15:57.030 --> 00:15:58.240
let's talk about this later.

00:15:58.240 --> 00:15:58.910
How could your wife

00:15:58.910 --> 00:16:00.240
hit a cop?

00:16:00.240 --> 00:16:00.670
Well,

00:16:01.080 --> 00:16:02.120
the station still needs...

00:16:02.120 --> 00:16:03.030
What?

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:05.270
Calm down!

00:16:05.790 --> 00:16:07.150
Who gave you the right to go?

00:16:07.150 --> 00:16:08.480
Are you her real father?

00:16:09.750 --> 00:16:10.790
Who are you?

00:16:10.790 --> 00:16:12.240
Who gave you the right to go?

00:16:12.240 --> 00:16:13.560
Who told you to go?

00:16:14.000 --> 00:16:15.480
I'll kill you if you dare!

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:19.240
I'll kill you and
that slut of a secretary of yours!

00:16:20.030 --> 00:16:20.750
He's been beaten up like that.

00:16:20.750 --> 00:16:22.150
We have to go check on him.

00:16:22.870 --> 00:16:24.200
Are you out of your mind?

00:16:24.550 --> 00:16:26.150
You just rush in when something happens.

00:16:26.150 --> 00:16:27.360
A couple's arguing

00:16:27.480 --> 00:16:28.630
and you go sticking your nose in.

00:16:28.630 --> 00:16:29.440
That iron's just as likely

00:16:29.440 --> 00:16:30.080
to smash your face

00:16:30.080 --> 00:16:31.280
as it is to smash mine.

00:16:36.720 --> 00:16:37.580
Actually, I...

00:16:38.460 --> 00:16:40.270
[I've been waiting for you for ages.
Where are you?- Beiping]

00:16:40.270 --> 00:16:41.000
Oh no.

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:43.220
Actually what?

00:16:43.910 --> 00:16:45.110
About this matter...

00:16:46.510 --> 00:16:47.970
What are you trying to say?

00:16:50.670 --> 00:16:52.030
You're really dawdling.

00:16:52.030 --> 00:16:53.630
You're not making any sense.

00:17:21.589 --> 00:17:22.450
What happened?

00:17:23.720 --> 00:17:24.310
What is it?

00:17:24.310 --> 00:17:25.680
What do you mean by "What?"

00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:27.030
Didn't we agree to
look at the place together?

00:17:27.030 --> 00:17:29.230
I've been waiting for you for two hours.

00:17:29.750 --> 00:17:30.440
Today?

00:17:32.110 --> 00:17:33.710
Didn't we agree on tomorrow?

00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:35.320
Are you playing dumb with me?

00:17:36.350 --> 00:17:37.550
Are you moving or not?

00:17:37.720 --> 00:17:38.720
Just tell me.

00:17:43.070 --> 00:17:44.070
Give me some time.

00:17:45.350 --> 00:17:46.950
There's a case in the hutong.

00:17:47.510 --> 00:17:48.510
What does it have to do

00:17:48.510 --> 00:17:49.440
with our moving?

00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:51.240
A girl

00:17:52.550 --> 00:17:53.240
was killed

00:17:53.310 --> 00:17:54.440
and thrown in a well.

00:17:55.550 --> 00:17:56.010
Then...

00:17:56.030 --> 00:17:57.350
That's more reason to move.

00:17:57.350 --> 00:17:58.410
Move immediately!

00:17:58.790 --> 00:18:00.640
When something serious happens,

00:18:00.640 --> 00:18:01.590
if I, a patrol officer,

00:18:01.590 --> 00:18:02.270
move out first,

00:18:02.270 --> 00:18:03.510
what will others think?

00:18:03.510 --> 00:18:04.510
So if you don't solve the case,

00:18:04.510 --> 00:18:05.840
I'm not allowed to move?

00:18:09.960 --> 00:18:11.030
Anyway, I can't stop

00:18:11.030 --> 00:18:12.090
what you want to do.

00:18:12.830 --> 00:18:15.200
But Dong's got his college entrance exams
coming up;

00:18:15.200 --> 00:18:16.800
let's not stir things up now.

00:18:33.440 --> 00:18:34.970
Why are you hanging on to it?

00:18:46.070 --> 00:18:49.380
The one who can't let go of you is me.

00:18:49.380 --> 00:18:50.630
[Hongqi store]

00:18:50.630 --> 00:18:54.230
The one who can't live without you is me.

00:18:59.350 --> 00:19:00.950
Do you want to listen with me?

00:19:02.400 --> 00:19:02.920
No, no.

00:19:03.440 --> 00:19:04.770
You go ahead and listen.

00:19:05.350 --> 00:19:06.210
I won't either.

00:19:13.000 --> 00:19:14.460
Do you ever write letters?

00:19:15.180 --> 00:19:16.640
If you need to reach me,

00:19:16.680 --> 00:19:17.550
you can call

00:19:17.590 --> 00:19:19.200
the Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:21.000
I don't really like phone calls;

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:21.680
they're

00:19:21.880 --> 00:19:23.540
too short, and nothing lasts.

00:19:23.590 --> 00:19:24.920
I like writing letters.

00:19:25.920 --> 00:19:27.270
How about this: let's make a deal.

00:19:27.270 --> 00:19:27.850
When the day comes that

00:19:27.850 --> 00:19:28.980
I leave this hutong,

00:19:29.310 --> 00:19:30.640
I'll write you a letter.

00:19:31.000 --> 00:19:32.660
By then, I'll probably be far,

00:19:32.830 --> 00:19:33.920
far away.

00:20:05.350 --> 00:20:05.880
Wang Lei,

00:20:06.920 --> 00:20:08.510
give me an update on your side.

00:20:08.510 --> 00:20:09.040
Alright.

00:20:10.270 --> 00:20:11.640
Liu Ke's stepfather, Liu Aijun,

00:20:11.640 --> 00:20:12.350
has a few people at his factory

00:20:12.350 --> 00:20:13.200
he's had conflicts with,

00:20:13.200 --> 00:20:14.160
but two of them were on business trips
at that time,

00:20:14.160 --> 00:20:15.160
and another is bedridden

00:20:15.160 --> 00:20:16.000
with a stroke.

00:20:16.720 --> 00:20:17.830
As for Liu Ke's biological father,

00:20:17.830 --> 00:20:18.270
[Victim's Biological Father: Zhou Weiping]

00:20:18.270 --> 00:20:19.880
Zhou Weiping has been
in and out of jail three times.

00:20:19.880 --> 00:20:20.920
He has prior convictions for theft

00:20:20.920 --> 00:20:22.030
and a traffic offense.

00:20:22.030 --> 00:20:23.550
He's currently
in the local detention center,

00:20:23.550 --> 00:20:24.780
but he doesn't really

00:20:24.780 --> 00:20:25.110
[Victim's Relationships-Known]
[Scene Record]

00:20:25.110 --> 00:20:26.310
know anyone locally.

00:20:26.770 --> 00:20:28.170
Where's the first scene?

00:20:28.480 --> 00:20:29.350
When it rained,

00:20:29.440 --> 00:20:31.030
the blood was washed away.

00:20:32.070 --> 00:20:32.870
That won't do.

00:20:32.920 --> 00:20:34.000
We still have to find it.

00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:35.270
Any info from Liu Ke's

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:36.110
family?

00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:38.660
We'll need to do more work.

00:20:39.270 --> 00:20:39.680
Oh,

00:20:40.310 --> 00:20:40.940
Liu Ke's school teacher

00:20:40.940 --> 00:20:41.510
[Victim's Relationships-Known]
[Scene Record]

00:20:41.510 --> 00:20:42.480
gave a lead.

00:20:42.590 --> 00:20:43.960
He said she received a call

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:44.510
at school

00:20:44.510 --> 00:20:45.440
that afternoon,

00:20:45.680 --> 00:20:47.160
but he doesn't know who it was from.

00:20:47.160 --> 00:20:48.830
The phone company's tracing it right now.

00:20:48.830 --> 00:20:49.510
Phone?

00:20:51.240 --> 00:20:52.570
When will they find out?

00:20:53.550 --> 00:20:54.510
I made the call.

00:20:56.440 --> 00:20:57.550
I asked her out.

00:20:58.720 --> 00:20:59.720
I saw her around 8 p.m.

00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:00.980
the night it happened.

00:21:06.510 --> 00:21:07.030
Sorry

00:21:07.350 --> 00:21:09.160
for holding up your investigation.

00:21:09.160 --> 00:21:09.590
Wait,

00:21:10.550 --> 00:21:11.590
you know her?

00:21:11.750 --> 00:21:12.350
No,

00:21:13.310 --> 00:21:14.110
I just met her.

00:21:14.790 --> 00:21:15.240
Well,

00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:16.540
you handle the case

00:21:17.000 --> 00:21:18.150
yourselves.

00:21:18.240 --> 00:21:20.040
We'll cooperate with you, okay?

00:21:20.200 --> 00:21:21.270
You should have told us earlier.

00:21:21.270 --> 00:21:21.330
You been playing us?

00:21:21.330 --> 00:21:22.220
[Victim's Relationships-Known]
[Scene Record]

00:21:28.270 --> 00:21:29.530
I'll kick you to death!

00:21:30.590 --> 00:21:32.110
I swear I'll kick you to death!

00:21:32.110 --> 00:21:32.750
Ran!

00:21:33.070 --> 00:21:33.640
Ran!

00:21:33.750 --> 00:21:34.510
What are you doing, Ran?

00:21:34.510 --> 00:21:34.920
Ran!

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:36.440
Is that how you handle things?

00:21:36.440 --> 00:21:36.920
Ran!

00:21:36.920 --> 00:21:37.960
Ran! Ran!

00:21:38.200 --> 00:21:39.660
Hold him! Let him sit down!

00:21:40.830 --> 00:21:41.240
Gosh.

00:21:41.240 --> 00:21:42.300
What are you doing?

00:21:42.880 --> 00:21:44.810
Don't make a fool of yourself here.

00:21:50.480 --> 00:21:51.830
Zhao Gan'e's mistake

00:21:52.310 --> 00:21:53.710
must be taken seriously.

00:21:53.750 --> 00:21:54.310
Song,

00:21:55.440 --> 00:21:56.240
but

00:21:57.680 --> 00:21:58.610
this is on me too.

00:21:59.480 --> 00:22:00.680
He mentioned it

00:22:01.200 --> 00:22:01.880
but I

00:22:02.550 --> 00:22:04.010
didn't take it seriously.

00:22:04.030 --> 00:22:04.640
Now that

00:22:05.240 --> 00:22:06.790
there's been a homicide,

00:22:07.640 --> 00:22:09.030
let's keep digging.

00:22:09.200 --> 00:22:09.790
Our station

00:22:09.790 --> 00:22:11.000
won't cover anyone.

00:22:11.510 --> 00:22:12.480
In a while, your Criminal Police Team

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:13.810
will pick one of our guys

00:22:13.880 --> 00:22:15.200
to take his statement.

00:22:16.920 --> 00:22:18.400
Is it an interview or an interrogation?

00:22:18.400 --> 00:22:19.680
Don't waste the others' time
with useless talk.

00:22:19.680 --> 00:22:21.010
Stop talking nonsense.

00:22:22.310 --> 00:22:23.770
Take his statement later.

00:22:25.640 --> 00:22:26.200
Ran,

00:22:28.550 --> 00:22:30.010
please put in more effort.

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:31.460
After all, this is…

00:22:31.830 --> 00:22:32.360
you know.

00:22:33.880 --> 00:22:34.920
I think we still have to

00:22:34.920 --> 00:22:35.830
follow the procedure.

00:22:35.830 --> 00:22:36.400
Yes.

00:22:38.200 --> 00:22:39.530
Don't interrogate him;

00:22:40.200 --> 00:22:41.460
just take a statement.

00:22:56.480 --> 00:22:57.080
Chief Zhu,

00:22:57.720 --> 00:22:59.180
assign someone else to me.

00:22:59.400 --> 00:23:00.460
I can't handle him.

00:23:00.510 --> 00:23:01.920
He's just a fool.

00:23:02.160 --> 00:23:03.420
He's a CPPSC graduate.

00:23:04.070 --> 00:23:04.680
You call him a fool,

00:23:04.680 --> 00:23:05.790
I'd say you're the fool.

00:23:05.790 --> 00:23:06.480
Fine.

00:23:06.680 --> 00:23:07.740
I'm the fool, okay?

00:23:07.790 --> 00:23:09.590
He's stubborn and thick-headed.

00:23:09.590 --> 00:23:10.920
What am I supposed to do?

00:23:13.030 --> 00:23:13.550
Ran,

00:23:13.550 --> 00:23:15.110
I'll tell you just two things.

00:23:15.110 --> 00:23:15.650
First,

00:23:15.880 --> 00:23:17.270
in all your ten years at the station,

00:23:17.270 --> 00:23:18.680
you've always played the fool.

00:23:18.680 --> 00:23:19.750
You've dodged every major case,

00:23:19.750 --> 00:23:20.960
and have I ever said a word about it?

00:23:20.960 --> 00:23:21.450
Second,

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:23.200
think back to

00:23:23.270 --> 00:23:24.720
when you were his age.

00:23:24.790 --> 00:23:25.750
What were you like?

00:23:25.750 --> 00:23:27.610
And how did your mentor treat you?

00:23:28.240 --> 00:23:29.170
Is being a mentor

00:23:29.480 --> 00:23:30.550
that easy?

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:36.440
[advanced unit]

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:36.690
We're just here to get the facts.

00:23:36.690 --> 00:23:39.440
[Speak openly. We'll listen.
Be honest. We'll understand.]

00:23:39.440 --> 00:23:41.270
How did you

00:23:41.640 --> 00:23:42.640
get to know Liu Ke?

00:23:44.310 --> 00:23:45.840
I interrogated her father—

00:23:45.880 --> 00:23:47.230
her biological father, Zhou Weiping.

00:23:47.230 --> 00:23:49.580
[Speak openly. We'll listen.
Be honest. We'll understand.]

00:23:49.680 --> 00:23:51.210
Then I got in touch with her.

00:23:51.960 --> 00:23:52.960
Zhou Weiping...

00:23:54.030 --> 00:23:54.880
Did you inform her

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:55.920
that the suspect was detained?

00:23:55.920 --> 00:23:57.920
Did you serve the detention notice?

00:24:00.160 --> 00:24:01.160
I didn't tell her.

00:24:01.680 --> 00:24:03.240
Then why did you call her?

00:24:05.030 --> 00:24:06.200
I want the suspect

00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:07.770
to cooperate with our work.

00:24:08.310 --> 00:24:09.270
I promised him

00:24:09.750 --> 00:24:11.640
I'd deliver a postcard to his daughter.

00:24:11.640 --> 00:24:12.510
What postcard?

00:24:13.200 --> 00:24:14.880
A postcard of The Little Tigers.

00:24:14.880 --> 00:24:16.080
What did she give you?

00:24:17.750 --> 00:24:18.960
What are you implying?

00:24:18.960 --> 00:24:19.750
You ask the suspect's daughter

00:24:19.750 --> 00:24:20.680
to meet you late at night.

00:24:20.680 --> 00:24:21.610
What do you mean?

00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:24.420
You were asking for
something, weren't you?

00:24:25.640 --> 00:24:26.110
Yes.

00:24:26.790 --> 00:24:28.190
I was asking for her life.

00:24:31.880 --> 00:24:32.640
We are classmates,

00:24:32.640 --> 00:24:33.510
same year.

00:24:33.790 --> 00:24:35.350
I'm not out to get you, okay?

00:24:35.750 --> 00:24:36.880
You're still young.

00:24:37.070 --> 00:24:38.510
Just lay all your cards on the table.

00:24:38.510 --> 00:24:39.720
You think I didn't tell you the truth,

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:40.200
right?

00:24:40.240 --> 00:24:41.200
You need to understand,

00:24:41.200 --> 00:24:42.440
I'm here to help you.

00:24:42.510 --> 00:24:43.750
This is my first case.

00:24:43.830 --> 00:24:45.270
This is also my first case.

00:24:45.270 --> 00:24:46.530
I don't need your help.

00:24:48.350 --> 00:24:50.270
Come on, let's go through this.

00:24:50.520 --> 00:24:50.570
You said you went out to meet her

00:24:50.570 --> 00:24:52.240
[Speak openly. We'll listen.
Be honest. We'll understand.]

00:24:52.240 --> 00:24:53.720
just to give her a postcard.

00:24:53.720 --> 00:24:54.720
But now you're telling me

00:24:54.720 --> 00:24:56.790
you two didn't even know
each other before?

00:24:56.790 --> 00:24:57.680
Buddy, if our roles were reversed,

00:24:57.680 --> 00:24:58.720
would you even believe that?

00:24:58.720 --> 00:24:59.750
Believe it or not.

00:25:03.070 --> 00:25:04.590
With an attitude like yours,

00:25:04.590 --> 00:25:07.350
you'll never make it into
the Criminal Police Team.

00:25:07.350 --> 00:25:08.210
Say that again.

00:25:09.640 --> 00:25:10.590
I said you'll never make it into

00:25:10.590 --> 00:25:11.790
the Criminal Police Team.

00:25:11.790 --> 00:25:13.720
And you'll never solve a real case!

00:25:14.510 --> 00:25:16.400
Whoa, what's going on with you two?

00:25:16.400 --> 00:25:18.000
Did you both wake up
on the wrong side of the bed?

00:25:18.000 --> 00:25:18.590
Do you still think

00:25:18.590 --> 00:25:19.650
you're in college?

00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:25.680
You're still on this?

00:25:28.640 --> 00:25:30.680
Someone saw
the two of them together yesterday.

00:25:30.680 --> 00:25:32.070
We have a timeline.

00:25:32.960 --> 00:25:33.590
Who?

00:25:34.070 --> 00:25:35.070
Zhao was seen with Liu Ke

00:25:35.070 --> 00:25:36.200
around 8-something PM.

00:25:36.200 --> 00:25:37.070
Someone saw it.

00:25:37.350 --> 00:25:39.550
The witness is giving his statement
right now.

00:25:39.550 --> 00:25:41.610
But the victim was killed after 10 PM.

00:25:42.310 --> 00:25:43.400
And at 10 o'clock,

00:25:43.720 --> 00:25:45.720
everyone in the station
saw Zhao right here with us!

00:25:45.720 --> 00:25:46.270
What the hell are you two

00:25:46.270 --> 00:25:47.470
still arguing about?

00:25:49.070 --> 00:25:49.900
Drop it.

00:25:50.830 --> 00:25:51.350
Well,

00:25:51.640 --> 00:25:52.720
sign the statement, then.

00:25:52.720 --> 00:25:53.790
If the witness can give a clear account,

00:25:53.790 --> 00:25:55.720
why do you even need his statement?

00:25:55.960 --> 00:25:56.640
Let's see which one of us

00:25:56.640 --> 00:25:57.750
puts the cuffs on the suspect first.

00:25:57.750 --> 00:25:59.110
See who puts the cuffs
on the suspect first.

00:25:59.110 --> 00:25:59.680
Fine.

00:26:05.610 --> 00:26:10.750
[2012]

00:26:10.750 --> 00:26:12.920
[Criminal Investigation Division,
Yanchuan City Police Department]

00:26:19.720 --> 00:26:20.240
Hello,

00:26:20.270 --> 00:26:21.480
who's the Captain?

00:26:22.160 --> 00:26:22.960
Captain Wang.

00:26:27.270 --> 00:26:27.920
Wang Lei?

00:26:28.110 --> 00:26:28.910
Isn't this...

00:26:30.030 --> 00:26:30.720
Zhao!

00:26:31.000 --> 00:26:31.800
Captain Wang.

00:26:32.030 --> 00:26:32.470
Zhao,

00:26:32.960 --> 00:26:33.960
why didn't you say

00:26:33.960 --> 00:26:35.530
before coming here?

00:26:35.720 --> 00:26:36.270
Captain Wang.

00:26:36.270 --> 00:26:36.960
Not bad.

00:26:37.240 --> 00:26:38.350
You haven't lost much hair.

00:26:38.350 --> 00:26:39.960
Clearly, you're not losing any sleep
over your work.

00:26:39.960 --> 00:26:41.310
You still remember me, Captain Wang?

00:26:41.310 --> 00:26:42.570
How could I forget you?

00:26:42.680 --> 00:26:44.200
I think you don't remember me.

00:26:44.200 --> 00:26:45.270
Come, have a seat.

00:26:45.480 --> 00:26:46.680
Li, get us some water.

00:26:51.350 --> 00:26:51.790
Zhao,

00:26:52.030 --> 00:26:53.960
what brings you here? Just tell me.

00:26:54.000 --> 00:26:54.680
I want to

00:26:54.920 --> 00:26:57.580
take a look at
the recent citywide case reports.

00:26:58.590 --> 00:26:59.680
Oh, come off it.

00:27:00.110 --> 00:27:01.550
You're living the easy life now;

00:27:01.550 --> 00:27:03.070
you don't have to
deal with people anymore.

00:27:03.070 --> 00:27:04.240
I'm almost jealous.

00:27:05.270 --> 00:27:07.160
I'm here about a case.

00:27:08.270 --> 00:27:09.680
It's a sequel to that old hutong one.

00:27:09.680 --> 00:27:11.210
Another one just popped up.

00:27:12.750 --> 00:27:13.750
Do you remember?

00:27:14.510 --> 00:27:16.440
It was the first case for both of us.

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:18.920
Which one was that again?

00:27:18.920 --> 00:27:20.120
Over on Limin Street.

00:27:21.110 --> 00:27:22.440
The perpetrator
didn't have time to finish.

00:27:22.440 --> 00:27:23.100
He got away.

00:27:23.590 --> 00:27:23.980
Fine.

00:27:24.030 --> 00:27:25.630
We'll check it for you later.

00:27:26.310 --> 00:27:28.510
Can I check the system?

00:27:29.790 --> 00:27:30.880
Well, this...

00:27:30.960 --> 00:27:32.720
I'd need authorization from higher up.

00:27:32.720 --> 00:27:33.050
Here.

00:27:33.180 --> 00:27:34.000
Have some water.

00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:34.640
Thank you.

00:27:38.480 --> 00:27:39.000
Wang,

00:27:40.030 --> 00:27:41.960
we're classmates. Please help me.

00:27:42.400 --> 00:27:42.880
Look,

00:27:43.750 --> 00:27:44.310
Zhao.

00:27:44.880 --> 00:27:47.410
It's not that I won't...
Just look at all this.

00:27:47.480 --> 00:27:48.880
These are four cases

00:27:49.030 --> 00:27:49.940
from today's call-outs.

00:27:49.940 --> 00:27:50.160
[Criminal Case File]

00:27:50.160 --> 00:27:51.960
These five are from the day before.

00:27:51.960 --> 00:27:52.640
And I still haven't even filed

00:27:52.640 --> 00:27:53.640
the double homicide case.

00:27:53.640 --> 00:27:55.240
And all these... and these...

00:27:55.240 --> 00:27:55.990
Well, I...

00:27:56.070 --> 00:27:56.870
Captain Wang,

00:27:57.480 --> 00:27:58.680
come on, do me a solid.

00:27:58.720 --> 00:27:59.520
It's not that,

00:28:00.030 --> 00:28:00.550
Zhao.

00:28:01.350 --> 00:28:03.200
You only have your one case over there.

00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:05.530
But here, I get this many
every single day.

00:28:09.640 --> 00:28:10.970
Alright, Captain Wang.

00:28:11.590 --> 00:28:13.510
I won't take up any more of your time.

00:28:13.510 --> 00:28:15.040
Sorry to have bothered you.

00:28:20.550 --> 00:28:21.070
Zhang,

00:28:21.160 --> 00:28:22.620
take this upstairs later.

00:28:22.680 --> 00:28:23.880
Got it, Captain Wang.

00:28:24.350 --> 00:28:24.960
Ran,

00:28:25.550 --> 00:28:27.110
if your son's on his last legs,

00:28:27.110 --> 00:28:28.240
why keep him around?

00:28:30.480 --> 00:28:31.740
Who says he's done for?

00:28:32.750 --> 00:28:33.880
He can pull through.

00:28:34.110 --> 00:28:35.000
But isn't it just suffering

00:28:35.000 --> 00:28:35.860
for both of you?

00:28:36.790 --> 00:28:37.590
Where are you

00:28:38.790 --> 00:28:39.790
taking him?

00:28:41.070 --> 00:28:43.440
Ran, you know the procedure
better than I do.

00:28:43.440 --> 00:28:46.300
He's officially property
of the municipal bureau.

00:28:50.110 --> 00:28:51.110
You call this

00:28:51.880 --> 00:28:52.610
"property"?

00:28:57.510 --> 00:28:59.310
How can you call him "property"?

00:29:02.310 --> 00:29:03.910
How many years has he served?

00:29:04.200 --> 00:29:05.600
He's got commendations.

00:29:06.160 --> 00:29:06.720
He does.

00:29:07.200 --> 00:29:08.400
But he's injured now.

00:29:08.680 --> 00:29:10.590
Even the vet said he won't get better.

00:29:10.590 --> 00:29:12.720
Keeping him around is just hard on you.

00:29:13.640 --> 00:29:14.680
Listen up,

00:29:16.640 --> 00:29:17.750
as long as I'm here,

00:29:20.750 --> 00:29:22.350
nobody is taking my son away.

00:29:36.790 --> 00:29:38.200
Mentor, how could you...

00:29:51.110 --> 00:29:51.830
Mentor,

00:29:54.680 --> 00:29:55.790
do you know

00:29:55.830 --> 00:29:57.430
where the new crime scene is?

00:29:59.510 --> 00:30:01.200
Right next to the relocation housing

00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:03.660
in our old neighborhood,
in the same hutong.

00:30:04.960 --> 00:30:06.220
Is this a coincidence?

00:30:06.880 --> 00:30:08.480
Who's got the guts to do this?

00:30:08.790 --> 00:30:10.190
He was harassing the girl

00:30:10.270 --> 00:30:12.270
by chasing her with a laser pointer.

00:30:14.310 --> 00:30:15.440
Is this harassment?

00:30:16.160 --> 00:30:17.720
I think that bastard

00:30:18.070 --> 00:30:18.830
is old

00:30:20.200 --> 00:30:21.000
and weak.

00:30:44.720 --> 00:30:45.590
I thought

00:30:46.920 --> 00:30:47.790
this bastard

00:30:48.790 --> 00:30:50.000
was already dead.

00:30:57.880 --> 00:30:59.340
I remember you used to say,

00:31:00.680 --> 00:31:03.010
"It's always the case that finds the man."

00:31:03.750 --> 00:31:05.550
Well, now the case has found you.

00:31:11.680 --> 00:31:14.930
[1994]

00:31:14.930 --> 00:31:16.970
[Inpatient Department]

00:31:21.110 --> 00:31:22.770
And you haven't changed a bit.

00:31:24.640 --> 00:31:25.110
Really?

00:31:27.350 --> 00:31:29.410
Don't start flattering me to my face.

00:31:30.070 --> 00:31:31.240
What should I say?

00:31:32.030 --> 00:31:32.400
Look,

00:31:32.400 --> 00:31:34.600
there's no need for all this between us.

00:31:36.270 --> 00:31:37.110
Alright,

00:31:37.310 --> 00:31:38.310
enough with the long face

00:31:38.310 --> 00:31:39.640
all day.

00:31:41.550 --> 00:31:42.400
A bullet

00:31:43.110 --> 00:31:44.370
couldn't take me down.

00:31:45.440 --> 00:31:46.510
You really think

00:31:47.110 --> 00:31:48.240
some lousy bacteria

00:31:48.270 --> 00:31:49.750
is gonna finish me off?

00:31:51.750 --> 00:31:52.350
Of course.

00:31:54.110 --> 00:31:54.960
Even bullets

00:31:54.960 --> 00:31:56.720
know to steer clear of your arteries.

00:31:56.720 --> 00:31:57.550
So,

00:31:59.720 --> 00:32:02.070
whenever you think of me in the future,

00:32:03.110 --> 00:32:04.480
I hope you remember the image of me,

00:32:04.480 --> 00:32:06.540
full of energy, catching criminals—

00:32:06.720 --> 00:32:08.250
that commanding presence.

00:32:10.070 --> 00:32:10.800
Absolutely.

00:32:13.750 --> 00:32:15.210
I could never forget that.

00:32:15.830 --> 00:32:16.830
You don't have to.

00:32:17.160 --> 00:32:19.830
Just remember what's worth remembering,
and let go of what's not.

00:32:19.830 --> 00:32:21.230
The key is not to force it.

00:32:23.920 --> 00:32:24.850
I won't force it.

00:32:27.510 --> 00:32:29.480
What I still don't get is...

00:32:31.880 --> 00:32:34.750
Are you really set on
staying a patrol officer

00:32:35.790 --> 00:32:38.450
and not coming back to
the Criminal Police Team?

00:32:39.920 --> 00:32:41.250
What would I go back for?

00:32:43.750 --> 00:32:45.880
Being a patrol officer suits me just fine.

00:32:45.880 --> 00:32:46.740
You're hiding.

00:32:47.510 --> 00:32:48.640
You're just hiding.

00:32:49.310 --> 00:32:51.040
I'm telling you, it's useless.

00:32:52.200 --> 00:32:53.960
The case will find you.

00:32:56.720 --> 00:32:58.920
It's always the case that finds the man.

00:33:00.510 --> 00:33:02.110
Not the man finding the case.

00:33:05.110 --> 00:33:05.970
I'm asking you,

00:33:06.680 --> 00:33:08.030
if a case finds you,

00:33:09.070 --> 00:33:10.000
will you take it?

00:33:13.070 --> 00:33:13.590
Mentor,

00:33:14.720 --> 00:33:15.240
I will.

00:33:18.200 --> 00:33:20.070
Don't just go through the motions.

00:33:20.070 --> 00:33:20.730
Do it right.

00:33:25.550 --> 00:33:26.550
I'll do it right.

00:33:29.200 --> 00:33:30.770
My back itches a bit;

00:33:30.830 --> 00:33:32.890
I can't really lift my arm to reach it.

00:33:33.960 --> 00:33:34.550
Okay.

00:33:34.720 --> 00:33:35.780
A little higher...

00:33:36.550 --> 00:33:37.610
Yeah, right there.

00:33:40.720 --> 00:33:41.400
Okay.

00:33:41.960 --> 00:33:42.440
Okay.

00:33:42.830 --> 00:33:43.360
Alright.

00:34:05.510 --> 00:34:06.920
What are you doing?

00:34:09.480 --> 00:34:10.480
Enough.

00:34:42.480 --> 00:34:43.110
Where's Ran?

00:34:43.110 --> 00:34:43.760
He's out.

00:34:44.280 --> 00:34:45.190
The coroner's office is asking

00:34:45.190 --> 00:34:46.630
why no one has come to
identify the body yet.

00:34:46.630 --> 00:34:47.710
What's going on?

00:34:50.480 --> 00:34:51.080
Chief Zhu,

00:34:52.150 --> 00:34:53.949
Captain Song is looking for you.

00:34:59.400 --> 00:34:59.800
Gan'e.

00:35:00.070 --> 00:35:00.480
Gan'e,

00:35:01.150 --> 00:35:02.610
stop messing around here.

00:35:02.710 --> 00:35:03.710
Go take care of the body identification

00:35:03.710 --> 00:35:05.480
for Huang Hui.

00:35:05.710 --> 00:35:08.910
Get it done, and it'll count as
an accomplishment for you.

00:35:29.880 --> 00:35:31.280
Auntie Huang Hui,

00:35:31.360 --> 00:35:34.220
I'm Zhao Gan'e
from the Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:35:36.400 --> 00:35:37.230
Actually, I'm responsible for

00:35:37.230 --> 00:35:38.110
Liu Ke's death.

00:35:39.670 --> 00:35:40.480
That night...

00:36:11.000 --> 00:36:11.510
Stop!

00:36:11.630 --> 00:36:12.190
Stop!

00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:25.730
What's going on?

00:36:25.920 --> 00:36:26.920
We just finished the rescue.

00:36:26.920 --> 00:36:27.520
It's fine.

00:36:29.710 --> 00:36:30.570
Where's Gan'e?

00:36:31.150 --> 00:36:31.810
Over there.

00:36:35.190 --> 00:36:36.280
You know, for what it's worth,
your apprentice

00:36:36.280 --> 00:36:37.480
is really something.

00:36:38.110 --> 00:36:40.240
He threw himself into the line of duty.

00:36:40.760 --> 00:36:41.490
So reckless.

00:36:42.030 --> 00:36:43.230
All he knows is to charge headfirst.

00:36:43.230 --> 00:36:43.920
Exactly.

00:36:44.190 --> 00:36:45.230
The mentor holds back,

00:36:45.230 --> 00:36:46.190
while the apprentice charges ahead.

00:36:46.190 --> 00:36:47.720
You two are a perfect match.

00:37:01.430 --> 00:37:03.920
[Save Food, Value Labor]

00:37:03.920 --> 00:37:04.360
Say it.

00:37:07.510 --> 00:37:08.110
Say what?

00:37:09.670 --> 00:37:10.550
Say what?

00:37:12.590 --> 00:37:13.030
Say it.

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:15.590
I'm sorry.

00:37:19.920 --> 00:37:21.120
I can barely hear you.

00:37:22.000 --> 00:37:23.260
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

00:37:27.480 --> 00:37:28.410
Can you hear him?

00:37:35.150 --> 00:37:36.010
Again. Louder.

00:37:43.630 --> 00:37:44.890
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

00:37:45.590 --> 00:37:46.840
Heard him.

00:37:47.920 --> 00:37:48.760
Ran, that's enough.

00:37:48.760 --> 00:37:49.550
We all heard him.

00:37:49.550 --> 00:37:50.550
Let him eat first.

00:37:51.480 --> 00:37:52.280
Listen to the leader.

00:37:52.280 --> 00:37:52.880
Let's eat.

00:37:53.070 --> 00:37:53.930
I'm not eating.

00:37:55.960 --> 00:37:58.440
If you don't eat well,
you can't solve the case.

00:37:58.440 --> 00:37:58.840
Eat.

00:38:12.230 --> 00:38:12.800
Hurry up.

00:38:42.030 --> 00:38:42.590
Mentor.

00:38:51.440 --> 00:38:52.500
I'm sorry, Mentor.

00:38:56.280 --> 00:38:56.880
Let's eat.

00:39:00.570 --> 00:39:01.960
[Save Food, Value Labor]

00:39:01.960 --> 00:39:02.760
Eat properly.

00:39:25.960 --> 00:39:26.990
Look at him,

00:39:27.510 --> 00:39:29.040
he can't handle spicy food.

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:30.900
It's okay.

00:39:30.960 --> 00:39:32.110
I wasn't used to it before either.

00:39:32.110 --> 00:39:33.110
But look at me now.

00:39:33.110 --> 00:39:35.970
Well, in that case,
you should join him and have one.

00:39:37.000 --> 00:39:37.800
I'll have one.

00:39:38.510 --> 00:39:39.400
Hope it burns!

00:39:52.440 --> 00:39:52.960
Chief,

00:39:54.000 --> 00:39:55.000
I didn't speak up earlier

00:39:55.000 --> 00:39:56.330
because I was afraid...

00:39:58.590 --> 00:39:59.920
I've let everyone down,

00:40:00.960 --> 00:40:02.490
and I've failed the victim.

00:40:02.920 --> 00:40:03.670
It's on me.

00:40:03.760 --> 00:40:04.710
It is on you.

00:40:05.190 --> 00:40:07.190
But we still need to solve this case.

00:40:08.490 --> 00:40:09.810
Can I stay on the case?

00:40:10.230 --> 00:40:11.280
You're a cop.

00:40:11.840 --> 00:40:13.300
Solving cases is your job.

00:40:14.880 --> 00:40:16.230
You've written your review;

00:40:16.230 --> 00:40:17.360
now go make it right.

00:40:17.550 --> 00:40:18.070
But that day,

00:40:18.070 --> 00:40:18.920
I asked her out.

00:40:18.920 --> 00:40:19.920
Stop right there.

00:40:21.150 --> 00:40:23.480
When I say the case is closed,
it's closed.

00:40:23.880 --> 00:40:24.760
This matter is over and done with.

00:40:24.760 --> 00:40:26.670
If anyone brings it up again,
they'll have me to answer to.

00:40:26.670 --> 00:40:27.190
Got it?

00:40:27.280 --> 00:40:28.940
-Got it.
-We won't mention it.

00:40:30.070 --> 00:40:30.670
By the way,

00:40:31.070 --> 00:40:31.870
you mentioned

00:40:32.110 --> 00:40:33.230
that Liu Ke had

00:40:33.280 --> 00:40:34.710
a habit of writing letters.

00:40:34.710 --> 00:40:35.190
Yes.

00:40:35.670 --> 00:40:36.710
Then where are the letters?

00:40:36.710 --> 00:40:38.110
Why haven't we found a single one?

00:40:38.110 --> 00:40:38.920
I heard

00:40:39.150 --> 00:40:40.550
Huang Hui was uncooperative before.

00:40:40.550 --> 00:40:42.320
But now that she's in the hospital,

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:44.450
Liu Aijun will definitely cooperate.

00:40:46.110 --> 00:40:48.240
I'll go to his house to find the letter.

00:40:49.920 --> 00:40:50.020
Get to work.

00:40:50.020 --> 00:40:50.590
[Save Food, Value Labor]

00:40:50.590 --> 00:40:51.250
Get to work.

00:40:56.480 --> 00:40:57.740
Look at the young ones,

00:40:57.920 --> 00:40:59.720
so focused on cracking the case.

00:40:59.800 --> 00:41:02.530
Can't say the same for
some of our older comrades.

00:41:04.480 --> 00:41:05.630
If you're not finishing those ribs,

00:41:05.630 --> 00:41:07.690
I'll gladly take them off your hands.

00:41:10.030 --> 00:41:11.840
So you're just going to keep playing dumb

00:41:11.840 --> 00:41:12.960
and being a stubborn asshole,

00:41:12.960 --> 00:41:13.560
is that it?

00:41:14.320 --> 00:41:15.590
They've all gone to look for the letters.

00:41:15.590 --> 00:41:17.360
Even if I went, I'd just be in the way.

00:41:17.360 --> 00:41:19.110
Then find something useful to do.

00:41:19.110 --> 00:41:20.280
Don't you dare just sit there
eating my ribs

00:41:20.280 --> 00:41:21.940
without pulling your weight.

00:41:22.440 --> 00:41:23.070
Why did this

00:41:23.070 --> 00:41:24.730
have to happen in my precinct?

00:41:24.920 --> 00:41:25.980
And no one heard it.

00:41:26.070 --> 00:41:27.320
Hurry up and investigate it.

00:41:27.320 --> 00:41:28.760
And do the alibi checks.

00:41:30.400 --> 00:41:31.510
But with so many officers
already assigned to the alibi checks,

00:41:31.510 --> 00:41:33.370
would one more make a difference?

00:41:33.670 --> 00:41:35.870
Well, how do you want to investigate it?

00:41:36.030 --> 00:41:37.360
Only someone with intimate knowledge of

00:41:37.360 --> 00:41:38.510
these hutongs

00:41:38.800 --> 00:41:40.070
would know about that dump site.

00:41:40.070 --> 00:41:41.630
And why was the manhole cover

00:41:41.630 --> 00:41:42.710
suddenly missing?

00:41:43.480 --> 00:41:45.210
That's all worth looking into.

00:41:45.550 --> 00:41:46.590
See?

00:41:47.030 --> 00:41:48.230
If you'd shown this initiative earlier,

00:41:48.230 --> 00:41:50.490
you would've saved me a lot of headaches.

00:41:50.710 --> 00:41:51.280
Just tell me

00:41:51.280 --> 00:41:53.010
what you need from the station.

00:41:55.000 --> 00:41:56.660
Give me the chicken leg first.

00:41:57.710 --> 00:41:58.400
Fine.

00:42:03.480 --> 00:42:04.440
I don't have

00:42:04.550 --> 00:42:05.680
any leads right now.

00:42:05.710 --> 00:42:07.170
I'll let you know when I do.

00:42:10.670 --> 00:42:15.930
[Save Food, Value Labor]

00:42:18.400 --> 00:42:19.600
Didn't you know Liu Ke

00:42:19.630 --> 00:42:20.960
usually wrote letters?

00:42:24.110 --> 00:42:25.280
I really had no idea.

00:42:25.840 --> 00:42:26.670
Her room door

00:42:26.710 --> 00:42:27.800
was always locked.

00:42:28.000 --> 00:42:29.110
She never let us in.

00:42:29.630 --> 00:42:30.890
Here, have some water.

00:42:31.000 --> 00:42:31.800
Don't bother.

00:42:37.000 --> 00:42:37.480
Zhang,

00:42:38.190 --> 00:42:38.760
stop looking.

00:42:38.760 --> 00:42:39.440
We've already searched that area.

00:42:39.440 --> 00:42:40.440
There's nothing.

00:42:41.150 --> 00:42:42.550
What about behind and

00:42:42.590 --> 00:42:43.840
under the bed?

00:42:44.030 --> 00:42:45.290
We looked everywhere.

00:43:10.510 --> 00:43:12.440
She really knew how to hide things.

00:43:23.760 --> 00:43:24.400
Get off!

00:43:26.190 --> 00:43:26.800
Hurry up.

00:43:27.360 --> 00:43:28.840
Well, what

00:43:28.840 --> 00:43:29.550
do you want?

00:43:32.700 --> 00:43:37.390
[Detention Cell] [Interrogation Room]

00:43:37.480 --> 00:43:37.680
[Water Room]

00:43:39.760 --> 00:43:41.630
Stop pushing. It's way too hot in there.

00:43:41.630 --> 00:43:42.760
It's nicer out here.

00:43:44.190 --> 00:43:45.050
It was me who...

00:43:47.590 --> 00:43:48.650
What are you doing?

00:43:51.800 --> 00:43:52.840
I told you to take the statements.

00:43:52.840 --> 00:43:54.640
Why are you just standing there?

00:43:57.960 --> 00:43:58.510
Mentor.

00:43:59.440 --> 00:44:00.150
You wanted to learn

00:44:00.150 --> 00:44:02.080
how to take the statements, right?

00:44:02.700 --> 00:44:03.920
Then go

00:44:04.070 --> 00:44:05.030
and conduct

00:44:05.440 --> 00:44:06.320
the alibi checks.

00:44:06.320 --> 00:44:07.550
But wasn't that already done?

00:44:07.550 --> 00:44:09.110
That was done by other officers.

00:44:09.110 --> 00:44:10.910
Are they obligated to teach you?

00:44:12.190 --> 00:44:13.030
I'm your

00:44:14.070 --> 00:44:14.670
mentor,

00:44:15.710 --> 00:44:17.040
so I don't have a choice.

00:44:20.920 --> 00:44:22.380
What's with your haircut?

00:44:25.550 --> 00:44:26.960
Early Aaron Kwok style.

00:44:27.710 --> 00:44:28.920
Stop talking nonsense.

00:44:28.920 --> 00:44:29.960
Where do you work?

00:44:30.440 --> 00:44:32.070
I work with my uncle in stocks.

00:44:32.070 --> 00:44:35.520
[Tool Room] [Interrogation Room]

00:44:36.320 --> 00:44:37.590
Put down for this "Aaron Kwok" here:

00:44:37.590 --> 00:44:38.550
Unemployed.

00:44:39.320 --> 00:44:40.800
How can I be unemployed?

00:44:41.960 --> 00:44:43.150
Sir,

00:44:43.230 --> 00:44:45.290
trading stocks is not unemployment.

00:45:04.960 --> 00:45:06.280
Why are you here again?

00:45:07.190 --> 00:45:08.320
What were you doing

00:45:08.360 --> 00:45:09.150
on the night of May 18th?

00:45:09.150 --> 00:45:11.960
I was writing to my pen friend at home.

00:45:12.360 --> 00:45:13.440
And who can verify that?

00:45:13.440 --> 00:45:14.190
My mom.

00:45:14.670 --> 00:45:15.870
Tell me your pen pal's

00:45:15.960 --> 00:45:16.590
name.

00:45:17.000 --> 00:45:18.150
Morning Mist.

00:45:18.590 --> 00:45:19.390
Which "Mist"?

00:45:19.590 --> 00:45:21.110
"Morning" as in Morning Mist.

00:45:21.110 --> 00:45:22.710
"Mist" as in Morning Mist.

00:45:23.030 --> 00:45:23.920
Have you met before?

00:45:23.920 --> 00:45:24.590
No.

00:45:25.480 --> 00:45:26.920
It's only perfect

00:45:27.190 --> 00:45:28.630
if we never meet.

00:45:29.190 --> 00:45:30.360
Understand?

00:45:34.550 --> 00:45:35.230
Hello.

00:45:35.760 --> 00:45:36.320
I'm an officer

00:45:36.320 --> 00:45:38.110
from Nanhuaishu Police Station.

00:45:38.110 --> 00:45:40.040
I'd like to ask you a few questions.

00:45:41.800 --> 00:45:42.480
Hello.

00:45:42.760 --> 00:45:43.400
Hello.

00:45:44.030 --> 00:45:45.190
Can you tell me

00:45:45.230 --> 00:45:46.960
what you were doing
on the night of May 18th?

00:45:46.960 --> 00:45:48.290
It was raining heavily.

00:45:48.880 --> 00:45:50.010
I was singing at home

00:45:52.360 --> 00:45:53.590
that night.

00:45:58.030 --> 00:45:58.840
And then?

00:45:58.960 --> 00:45:59.630
I'm sorry.

00:45:59.880 --> 00:46:00.800
I'm going out.

00:46:07.880 --> 00:46:09.210
I haven't finished yet.

00:46:10.190 --> 00:46:10.840
Sorry.

00:46:11.000 --> 00:46:12.260
I have something to do.

00:46:17.890 --> 00:46:22.570
[Map of Nanhuaishu Streets and Alleys]

00:46:29.780 --> 00:46:31.570
[Record of Inquiry]

00:46:37.670 --> 00:46:38.500
[Map of Nanhuaishu Streets and Alleys]

00:46:42.630 --> 00:46:43.290
Do it again.

00:46:43.670 --> 00:46:44.590
Can you at least tell me

00:46:44.590 --> 00:46:45.520
what I did wrong?

00:46:47.000 --> 00:46:48.460
I'll give you one example:

00:46:48.800 --> 00:46:49.550
the format is incorrect.

00:46:49.550 --> 00:46:50.750
What's wrong with it?

00:46:50.760 --> 00:46:52.220
You think this is an essay?

00:46:52.320 --> 00:46:54.110
It needs to be in a strict
question-and-answer format, at least.

00:46:54.110 --> 00:46:54.670
Why?

00:46:57.000 --> 00:46:58.130
Those are the rules.

00:46:59.150 --> 00:47:00.550
Can't I just fix it, then?

00:47:01.190 --> 00:47:03.840
The statements need
to be conducted again as well.

00:47:03.840 --> 00:47:04.840
What's wrong with it?

00:47:04.840 --> 00:47:06.040
Everything is wrong.

00:47:12.850 --> 00:47:16.290
[Love is on the left, compassion on the right,
walking on both sides of life.]

00:47:21.070 --> 00:47:23.520
[To: Liu Ke, Nanhuaishu Street,
Yanchuan City]

00:47:27.480 --> 00:47:29.280
This doesn't look right either.

00:47:40.760 --> 00:47:42.690
Write it again with your left hand.

00:47:49.230 --> 00:47:49.800
Mentor,

00:47:51.320 --> 00:47:51.920
wait.

00:47:52.960 --> 00:47:54.290
Take another look at it.

00:48:10.670 --> 00:48:11.840
Why did you tear it up again?

00:48:11.840 --> 00:48:12.500
Do it again.

00:48:13.000 --> 00:48:14.550
Maybe you could come with me?

00:48:14.550 --> 00:48:17.080
If I go, does that count as
showing your skill?

00:48:17.320 --> 00:48:18.360
What's wrong with it this time?

00:48:18.360 --> 00:48:18.960
Listen up,

00:48:19.440 --> 00:48:21.040
I'll only show you this once.

00:48:21.280 --> 00:48:22.110
You've conducted this statement

00:48:22.110 --> 00:48:23.240
multiple times now.

00:48:23.800 --> 00:48:24.920
On the night of the incident,

00:48:24.920 --> 00:48:25.800
there was loud

00:48:26.230 --> 00:48:27.070
dog barking—

00:48:27.360 --> 00:48:28.280
some neighbors heard it,

00:48:28.280 --> 00:48:29.140
others didn't.

00:48:29.550 --> 00:48:31.150
Some people in the same house

00:48:31.190 --> 00:48:31.840
heard it,

00:48:31.880 --> 00:48:33.610
others in the same room didn't.

00:48:33.760 --> 00:48:35.710
You can't just read the words on the page.

00:48:35.710 --> 00:48:37.000
Use your head

00:48:37.840 --> 00:48:39.500
and think about what it means.

00:48:40.190 --> 00:48:41.360
I'll do it again.

00:48:41.550 --> 00:48:42.630
Look what time it is.

00:48:42.630 --> 00:48:43.480
Do you think people don't sleep?

00:48:43.480 --> 00:48:44.630
The golden 72 hours.

00:48:49.880 --> 00:48:55.920
[Pharmacy]

00:49:03.150 --> 00:49:03.920
Ran.

00:49:04.710 --> 00:49:05.510
Get me

00:49:05.920 --> 00:49:07.030
two boxes of Hawthorn Pills.

00:49:07.030 --> 00:49:07.830
What's wrong?

00:49:08.000 --> 00:49:09.070
Does your kid have food stagnation?

00:49:09.070 --> 00:49:10.510
I'll also grab some Digestive Tablets.

00:49:10.510 --> 00:49:11.000
I...

00:49:11.760 --> 00:49:13.220
Guess I'm just that bored.

00:49:14.440 --> 00:49:16.400
You're actually getting them for me?

00:49:16.400 --> 00:49:17.480
Show me the ledger.

00:49:24.150 --> 00:49:25.190
I want to find out

00:49:25.840 --> 00:49:27.150
who in the precinct

00:49:27.190 --> 00:49:27.550
[Sleeping Pill Sales Record-April 1994]

00:49:27.550 --> 00:49:28.770
has been losing sleep
since this big incident.

00:49:28.770 --> 00:49:29.440
[Names: Ergou, He, Tiantian, Bing]

00:49:29.440 --> 00:49:30.510
Everyone who bought sleeping pills

00:49:30.510 --> 00:49:31.440
is registered.

00:49:33.030 --> 00:49:33.230
[Sleeping Pill Sales Record-March 1994]

00:49:33.230 --> 00:49:34.000
Who is this?

00:49:34.130 --> 00:49:35.330
Buying them so often?

00:49:35.960 --> 00:49:36.320
Ran,

00:49:36.440 --> 00:49:37.110
try this.

00:49:37.760 --> 00:49:38.920
Try it.

00:49:39.030 --> 00:49:39.760
What is this?

00:49:41.760 --> 00:49:43.070
Who are you trying to embarrass here?

00:49:43.070 --> 00:49:44.110
Wait, bro,

00:49:44.510 --> 00:49:45.880
don't beat around

00:49:46.150 --> 00:49:47.070
the bush with me.

00:49:47.070 --> 00:49:48.880
Look, even your wife
is being open about it.

00:49:48.880 --> 00:49:49.590
Beiping?

00:49:50.630 --> 00:49:51.560
What did she buy?

00:49:52.060 --> 00:49:53.360
[Family Planning Products Sales Record
-May 1994]

00:49:53.360 --> 00:49:54.670
She asked me to do her a favor,

00:49:54.670 --> 00:49:56.030
pick up a few boxes for her.

00:49:56.030 --> 00:49:56.840
Don't worry.

00:49:57.280 --> 00:49:58.430
I just noted the quantity sold.

00:49:58.430 --> 00:49:58.630
[Family Planning Products Sales Record
-May 1994]

00:49:58.630 --> 00:49:59.490
Bought so many?

00:50:00.090 --> 00:50:00.880
It's not like I can

00:50:00.880 --> 00:50:02.080
use that many myself.

00:50:03.280 --> 00:50:03.760
Enough.

00:50:03.960 --> 00:50:05.020
Lend me the ledger.

00:50:07.220 --> 00:50:08.110
[Indian Mystic Oil]

00:50:27.880 --> 00:50:30.080
What time is it? Why are you back so late?

00:50:31.480 --> 00:50:33.080
I came back to get something.

00:50:33.320 --> 00:50:34.550
Get what?

00:50:39.400 --> 00:50:40.030
Well,

00:50:41.400 --> 00:50:43.400
Have you bought anything recently?

00:50:54.510 --> 00:50:55.230
You know,

00:50:56.190 --> 00:50:57.960
if you buy so much and don't use it,

00:50:57.960 --> 00:50:58.960
it's such a waste.

00:51:06.150 --> 00:51:06.880
Go to sleep.

00:51:22.230 --> 00:51:27.180
[Household Register]

00:51:29.790 --> 00:51:31.610
[Work Notes]

00:51:31.610 --> 00:51:33.030
[condom]